    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Interesting ! Normally for the player who disconnected the replay must end when he goes out.\nI will see that. \n\nEdit: Upon reflection it is normal, the replay doesn't contain the last frame for other players and my logic block the default int.MaxValue. If units terminate the last order it's (I think) ok contrary to do random things. Nevertheless such cases must be blocked or warned. \n\nEdit 2: possibility to add #hacktoberfest to PR label ?\n"
